I visited [[Tōkyō]] again in the second full week of June 2023 with a group of
11 friends. Some went to Kyōtō on a day trip, I did not and stayed in the
capital city for the full week. I have been here before when I studied at
[[Sophia_University]] for a semester in the Summer.

I host some of the pictures from this trip [in a
gallery](https://gallery.wesl.ee/gallery/Tokyo23) on a separate site.

